PTX Fence-SC-Atom
"Figure 6 of https://dl.acm.org/doi/epdf/10.1145/3297858.3304043"
{
x=0;
y=0;
P0:r0=0;
P1:r1=0;
}
 P0@cta 0,gpu 0         | P1@cta 1,gpu 0         ;
 st.relaxed.gpu x, 1    | st.relaxed.gpu y, 1    ;
 fence.sc.gpu           | fence.sc.gpu           ;
 ld.relaxed.gpu r0, y   | ld.relaxed.gpu r1, x   ;
~exists
(P0:r0 == 0 /\ P1:r1 == 0)